page.title: 07HOBBIES
page.content: SWIMMING IS THE MOST POPULAR HOBBY BECAUSE PEOPLE LIKE THE DIFFERENT STROKES.BALLET IS ANOTHER HOBBY PEOPLE LIKE BECAUSE OF ALL THE DANCES THEY DO,LIKE THE POLKA AND OTHER DANCES. LOTS OF PEOPLE LIKE GYM AS WELL BECAUSE THEY LIKE DOING HAND-STANDS AND CART-WHEELS AND LOTS OF OTHER THINGS. PEOPLE LIKE PLAYING ON THE COMPUTER BECAUSE OF THE GAMES LIKE GRANNYS-GARDEN AND FATHER- CHRISMAS.SOME PEOPLE LIKE DRAWING AND PAINTING THINGS LIKE RABBITS,BIRDS AND ANIMALS FROM THE ZOO.PEOPLE LIKE RIDING THEIR BIKES DOWN THE ROADS AND ALONG TRACKS. SOME PEOPLE COLLECT FOREIGN DOLLS FROM PLACES LIKE SCOTLAND,WALES,CHINA,SPAIN AND GERMANY AND LOTS OF PLACES LIKE THAT.PEOPLE LIKE DOLLS BECAUSE OF THEIR COSTUMES.
